SkyDrive helper is a simple class that makes using SkyDrive backup easier. It's desing for backuping specified number of files from and to Isolated Storage. 

//It's build on top of SkyDrive backup sample by Andrew Bares (http://wmpoweruser.com/developers-use-skydrive-to-backup-app-data/)

